      <title>欧盟债券在 MSCI 拒绝将其纳入主权指数后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/eu-debt-falls-after-bonds-not-added-to-msci-government-indexes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟债券周四下跌，因市场对欧盟债券将很快被纳入主要主权基准的押注遭遇早期打击。]]></description>
